7 SETTING WHERE A CHILD IS RESIDING; AND
8 (IV) A REPRESENTATIVE OF THE HOSPITAL WHERE THE CHILD IS
9 CONSIDERED A PEDIATRIC HOSPITAL OVERSTAY PATIENT.
