16 NECESSARY; AND
17 (3) SECURE IMMEDIATE PLACEMENT IN AVAILABLE LICENSED
18 SETTINGS.
19 (E) WHEN A PLACEMENT TEAM IS CONVENED, THE PLACEMENT TEAM
20 SHALL MEET EACH DAY UNTIL A PLACEMENT FOR THE CHILD IS LOCATED.
